QUESTION: Which League had the most matches end as draw in the 2016 season? most matches end as draw refers to MAX(SUM(home_team_goal = away_team_goal)); 2016 season refers to season = '2015/2016';
Generate just the question starting it with 'start_sql' and ending the sql with 'end_sql' nothing else is allowed on the response. Do not add any explanations or comments.
start_sql
SELECT l.name AS league_name, COUNT(*) AS draw_matches
FROM table_0 m
JOIN table_1 l ON m.column_1 = l.column_0
WHERE m.season = '2015/2016' AND m.home_team_goal = m.away_team_goal
GROUP BY l.name
ORDER BY draw_matches DESC
LIMIT 1;
end_sql

QUESTION: List the top 5 leagues in ascending order of the number of goals made in all seasons combined. number of goals made in all seasons combine = SUM(home_team_goal, away_team_goal);
Generate just the question starting it with 'start_sql' and ending the sql with 'end_sql' nothing else is allowed on the response. Do not add any explanations or comments.
start_sql
SELECT l.name AS league_name, SUM(m.home_team_goal + m.away_team_goal) AS total_goals
FROM table_1 AS l
JOIN table_2 AS s ON l.column_1 = s.column_1
JOIN table_3 AS m ON s.column_2 = m.column_0
GROUP BY l.name
ORDER BY total_goals ASC
LIMIT 5;
